      ************************** ECSRA1 **
     FECSPWA1 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FECSPL07 IF  E           K        DISK
     FGCQPL14 IF  E           K        DISK
     FECSWPA1 O   F     100            DISK
      *
     E                    ER      1   3 70               d[ｰxｮﾈｰﾆﾞ
      *
      ***
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           EQKAT1
     C                     KFLD           EQKAT2
